--- the other side of the trade: a range scan over one hour ---

=== RANGE-partitioned: how many partitions does the plan touch? ===
                                                                          QUERY PLAN                                                                          
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Aggregate
   ->  Seq Scan on ev_range_07 ev_range
         Filter: ((occurred_at >= '2025-07-15 00:00:00+00'::timestamp with time zone) AND (occurred_at < '2025-07-15 01:00:00+00'::timestamp with time zone))
(3 rows)

partition scan nodes:
1

